com.b2international.snowowl.dsl

Class ESCGRewriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.b2international.snowowl.dsl.ESCGRewriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    QueryParser, QueryRewriter<org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject>

    public class ESCGRewriter
extends Object
implements QueryParser
    Rewrites an ESCG parse tree and produces to "Query AST" form. The rewrite makes implicit "is_a" relationships explicit from the "concepts" part of the CGS expression (i.e. the terms before the ':').
